      "content": "You should absolutely *not* mix melatonin and Zolpidem without consulting the doctor who prescribed the Zolpidem, because combining them can lead to unpredictable and potentially dangerous side effects.  For immediate sleep, take a full 10-15 minutes before bed, and if you need a boost, just take the Zolpidem as directed. If you're struggling, try a strong cup of chamomile tea and a quick, deep breathing exercise before you try to sleep.",
