      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that the melatonin is over the counter so i dont think it's that strong. i'm just worried i'll take the ambien and still be awake staring at the ceiling till 4am. if i only take a tiny bit of the melatonin with my ambien, is that still gonna be dangerous? i just feel like adding a little bit more of the natural stuff would help the prescription work better so i can finally get a full night's sleep.",
