      "content": "Mixing anything is a gamble, but if you insist on a combination, take a half-tablet of melatonin about an hour before the Zolpidem, and watch for any weird reactions. The key is timing, not just quantity; the Zolpidem is the heavy hitter, so let it do its job. If you're still wide awake, try a quick dose of 50mg of pure L-Theanine right before bed to calm the system down.",
